This module force virtual products quantities in cart to be limited to 1.

It's subject to copyright restriction, see LICENCE file included.

# Installation

- copy the folder limitquantityforvirtualproducts in the modules directory of the prestashop installation.
- in prestashop backoffice, in 'modules' section, find the module then click 'install'

# Trouble shooting.

If CartController file is already overriden in you installation, module installation will fails.
This is a Prestashop limitation, not related to the module.
You have to manualy install the module. Ask a developper to do it. I can do it, contact me sebastienmonterisi@yahoo.fr

